com.quinsoft.zeidon

Class DeserializeOi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.quinsoft.zeidon.DeserializeOi

  • public class DeserializeOi
extends Object
    Encapsulates all options available for activating OI's from streams and offers convenience methods activate() and activateFirst().

    dgc
